X: {4, 8, 12, 16, 20}
Y: {2, 4, 6, 8, 10}

Dr. Smith hypothesizes that as the number of years since deployment increases, the level of PTSD symptoms decreases. To test this hypothesis, he decides to calculate the covariance between these two sets of data. 

